Lynda Obst, the owner of Lynda Obst 
Productions, says when DVDs collapsed, Hollywood profit margins 
were cut in half. Obst talks with Bloomberg's  Tom Keene , Scarlet
Fu and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:31
 